Output demo/recording/mvp_cli.gif
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1300
Set Height 520
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 16
Type "# SovereignSec-AI MVP: audit a repo, fully local, proof-carrying findings"
Enter
Sleep 600ms
Type 'PATH="$PWD/.venv/bin:$PATH" PYTHONPATH=. .venv/bin/python -m sscai audit demo/seeded_repo'
Enter
Sleep 4s
